text: Willoughby is an electoral district of New South Wales. It was created in 1894, abolished in 1920, recreated in 1927, reabolished in 1988 and recreated again in 1991. It is a conservative electorate. Willoughby is located on Sydney's North Shore. ==Election results== The swings above are calculated from the 2022 Willoughby state by-election. ==References== Willoughby
